<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>

<ThingDef ParentName="ApparelMakeableBase">
    <defName>Nr_CatJacket</defName>
    <label>전투 재킷</label>
    <description>오픈 재킷과 반바지가 한 세트인 의상입니다. 겉보기와 달리 무척 튼튼합니다.</description>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Things/Apparel/CatJacket/CatJacket</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
    </graphicData>
    <costStuffCount>225</costStuffCount>
    <stuffCategories>
      <li>Fabric</li>
      <li>Leathery</li>
    </stuffCategories>
    <thingCategories>
      <li>NrApparel</li>
    </thingCategories>
    <statBases>
			<MaxHitPoints>300</MaxHitPoints>
			<WorkToMake>30000</WorkToMake>
      <Mass>4.2</Mass>
      <StuffEffectMultiplierArmor>0.4</StuffEffectMultiplierArmor>
	  <ArmorRating_Sharp>0.45</ArmorRating_Sharp>
	  <ArmorRating_Blunt>0.2</ArmorRating_Blunt>
      <StuffEffectMultiplierInsulation_Cold>1</StuffEffectMultiplierInsulation_Cold>
      <StuffEffectMultiplierInsulation_Heat>1.5</StuffEffectMultiplierInsulation_Heat>
      <EquipDelay>2</EquipDelay>
    </statBases>
    <apparel>
      <bodyPartGroups>
        <li>Torso</li>
        <li>Neck</li>
        <li>Shoulders</li>
		<li>Legs</li>
      </bodyPartGroups>
      <wornGraphicPath>Things/Apparel/CatJacket/CatJacket</wornGraphicPath>
      <layers>
        <li>OnSkin</li>
		<li>Middle</li>
		<li>Shell</li>
      </layers>
      <tags>
        <li>Nyaron_IndustrialCustom</li>
      </tags>
      <defaultOutfitTags>
        <li>Worker</li>
      </defaultOutfitTags>
    </apparel>
    <colorGenerator Class="ColorGenerator_StandardApparel" />
  </ThingDef>
</Defs>
